Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.87,0:00:49.82,opzw,NTP,0,0,0,,托付给大地的我们的旅程
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.44,0:00:56.68,opzw,NTP,0,0,0,,宛如呼啸而过的旋风
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.14,0:01:00.20,opzw,NTP,0,0,0,,向命运低头
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.20,0:01:04.61,opzw,NTP,0,0,0,,蜷缩在角落真是无趣
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.61,0:01:08.88,opzw,NTP,0,0,0,,逊到极点！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.45,0:01:12.45,opzw,NTP,0,0,0,,弄巧成拙
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.96,0:01:18.34,opzw,NTP,0,0,0,,后悔也一定是作茧自缚
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.34,0:01:21.31,opzw,NTP,0,0,0,,绝对、有志者事竟成！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.46,0:01:27.87,opzw,NTP,0,0,0,,为大浪吞没
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.20,0:01:34.35,opzw,NTP,0,0,0,,不如随波逐流
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.71,0:01:37.43,opzw,NTP,0,0,0,,产生于误会的梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.57,0:01:40.64,opzw,NTP,0,0,0,,落空的期待
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.64,0:01:46.40,opzw,NTP,0,0,0,,只要坚信  终有一天能够得到！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.15,0:01:53.30,opzw,NTP,0,0,0,,跨出这一步出发吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.57,0:02:00.26,opzw,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,1500)}宛如自由飞舞的旋风
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.46,0:21:55.36,edzw,NTP,0,0,0,,被风吹拂着　乘风飘扬的心之风帆
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.46,0:22:00.01,edzw,NTP,0,0,0,,心情忐忑不安　然后 lose my way
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.28,0:22:03.15,edzw,NTP,0,0,0,,你一直陪伴着我就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.28,0:22:07.62,edzw,NTP,0,0,0,,这样也不错　so I go together
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.75,0:22:11.02,edzw,NTP,0,0,0,,不用什么天气预报
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.22,0:22:13.58,edzw,NTP,0,0,0,,完全由心情来决定
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.78,0:22:16.21,edzw,NTP,0,0,0,,什么都不用担心
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.44,0:22:18.98,edzw,NTP,0,0,0,,交给我吧！ 自由自在
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.21,0:22:21.29,edzw,NTP,0,0,0,,把鞋子抛上去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.49,0:22:23.96,edzw,NTP,0,0,0,,‘put a wish’ 绝对会放晴 ！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.20,0:22:26.64,edzw,NTP,0,0,0,,但是结果却是…　I'm looking at nothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.70,0:22:29.31,edzw,NTP,0,0,0,,再让我重新抛一次！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.31,0:22:33.47,edzw,NTP,0,0,0,,偶尔试一次赌注吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.83,0:22:37.17,edzw,NTP,0,0,0,,想拜托给你试试
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.07,0:22:41.80,edzw,NTP,0,0,0,,追赶着飒爽　to fly
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.25,0:22:44.51,edzw,NTP,0,0,0,,能见到万里晴空　the sky
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.71,0:22:46.48,edzw,NTP,0,0,0,,一直相信你的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.15,0:22:49.29,edzw,NTP,0,0,0,,然后 make my way
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.48,0:22:52.19,edzw,NTP,0,0,0,,突然间伸出的你的手
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.49,0:22:57.01,edzw,NTP,0,0,0,,会变成无敌的存在　so I go together
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.76,0:23:05.06,edzw,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,1800)}星空无比美丽　明天一定也会是晴天吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.28,0:00:05.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,才不会把小飒交给你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.36,0:00:10.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这人  这人是我的…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.31,0:00:12.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我重要的管家啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.95,0:00:17.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,管家乃侍奉之人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.17,0:00:20.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,管家乃照料之人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.47,0:00:26.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,管家乃打理主人诸般事宜的正式守护者
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.19,0:00:28.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.32,0:00:33.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这是少年为了某位少女而拼上性命全力战斗的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.51,0:00:36.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,超级管家战斗物语
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.39,0:00:39.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,愿意做我的管家吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.41,0:00:41.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是的  我乐意至极  大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.26,0:00:41.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你是谁啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.46,0:02:16.98,title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,0)\fsp0\pos(352,375)}\N\N送达时间29分\N请按规定支付费用……\N这是遥远的上世纪的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.35,0:02:19.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,故事追溯到早晨
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.03,0:02:21.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,绫崎飒  出现
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.34,0:02:25.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,醒来的  Make up！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.34,0:02:25.32,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,（此姿势出自「美少女战士」）
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.07,0:02:28.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不是这个
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.57,0:02:32.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  是这个啦  这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.89,0:02:35.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,前回被伊澄家所收留的小飒
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.66,0:02:38.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,又再次回到三千院家了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.44,0:02:38.77,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,（人像出自「北斗神拳」的主人公健次郎）
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.98,0:02:42.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,以后也要全心全意为大小姐服务
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.87,0:02:46.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这么快就呼唤我了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.92,0:02:51.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…大小姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.05,0:02:53.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,呐  小飒
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.20,0:02:53.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.93,0:02:54.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,问你一件事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.08,0:02:57.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你有失忆过吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.59,0:02:59.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,咦  失忆？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.99,0:03:02.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀…没有这方面的经验
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.88,0:03:06.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,其实是她又想冲击漫画新人奖了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.83,0:03:12.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  我这回想要挑战失忆这个漫画中最俗的手法
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.47,0:03:16.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对  例如被疼爱的管家背叛而奔出家门
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.12,0:03:17.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,被马车所撞之类
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.49,0:03:19.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,或者是Glod sleep？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.97,0:03:22.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,确实这种捏它先例举不胜举
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.15,0:03:24.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不过  反过来想
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.68,0:03:26.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,正因如此  才有尝试的价值
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.86,0:03:27.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哦…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.83,0:03:33.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因此  好像在思考创作失忆的主题
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.69,0:03:37.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一直都没有灵感啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.11,0:03:40.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 就由我去亘的店
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.75,0:03:43.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,去借几盘有失忆捏它的作品来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.19,0:03:47.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是…是啊  确实…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.16,0:03:48.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,无论什么都请吩咐我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.20,0:03:51.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我是大小姐忠实的管家
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.39,0:03:53.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小飒…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.51,0:03:55.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那么  我去了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.68,0:04:01.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,玛莉亚  果然小飒是宇宙第一可靠的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.39,0:04:03.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…是呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.31,0:04:06.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,希望不要再遇到什么危险就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.40,0:04:15.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因为上回的豪言
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.66,0:04:19.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小飒的生命似乎受到了危险
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.26,0:04:21.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,也去告诉其他候补者
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.55,0:04:23.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,想要三千院家遗产的话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.51,0:04:26.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就必须将其管家绫崎飒打倒再说
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.14,0:04:28.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,Hi  绫崎飒
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.14,0:04:31.07,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,（基鲁巴特的机器身体出自「ゲゲゲの鬼太郎」，\N头部的圆球出自「机动战士高达」登场的RB-79 Ball）
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.91,0:04:31.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如何  又见面了？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.26,0:04:32.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这声音是…基鲁巴特
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.08,0:04:37.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,三千院的遗产当然是我的了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.38,0:04:38.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.62,0:04:41.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你也真是个不长记性的人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.14,0:04:41.78,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,（基鲁巴特的cos来自「Yatterman」中登场的恶役三人组女boss中的ドロンジョ(多弄姿)）
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.88,0:04:44.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你居然自己钻进移动的棺材里
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.18,0:04:46.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这…这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.27,0:04:52.69,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,今天的爱情占卜
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.54,0:04:52.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,呃…今天的幸运物是  批萨
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.94,0:04:55.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,幸运地点是  公园
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.24,0:04:59.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,也许会有和白马王子的一段美丽的邂逅在等着你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.86,0:05:02.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这难道是…能与小飒见面？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.68,0:05:07.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,话说…不可能有那么巧的事情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.68,0:05:14.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小飒  不会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.79,0:05:16.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,西泽同学
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.94,0:05:19.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶  放开我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.01,0:05:24.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小飒
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.32,0:05:25.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真的是小飒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.08,0:05:27.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不…不过  你在做什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.94,0:05:30.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么在与那个战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.20,0:05:31.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不是…那个
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.54,0:05:32.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,绫崎飒
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.25,0:05:35.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,觉悟吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.55,0:05:38.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,等下再解释
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.75,0:05:40.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,总之  先逃离这里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.71,0:05:43.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好…好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.26,0:05:48.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这种构思不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.15,0:05:53.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,别说被杂志刊登了  就连特质网格稿纸五十张也不能期待
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.19,0:05:56.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小凪  是咲夜来的电话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.86,0:05:58.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,现在无信号  再见
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.19,0:05:59.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.50,0:06:01.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那个  我家的笨蛋哥哥在你那边吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.43,0:06:03.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋哥哥？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.76,0:06:05.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是指基鲁巴特吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.51,0:06:09.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那个傻子用我的名义好像租了不得了的兵器
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.03,0:06:11.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,兵…兵器？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.58,0:06:12.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对对对
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.09,0:06:15.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀  客人  还是那么不「兵器」
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.09,0:06:15.65,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,（把景气错说成兵器）
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.74,0:06:16.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是受不了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.09,0:06:18.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那应该读景气  笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.72,0:06:20.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,总之  先不说这个
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.69,0:06:23.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,反正又是去找那负债管家了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.44,0:06:25.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要是去做什么坏事的话  就委婉地让他回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.96,0:06:27.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小凪？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.98,0:06:30.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,既然是小飒的事情  应该不用担心  不过…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.61,0:06:33.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,叫上保镖
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.89,0:06:35.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,去找小飒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.56,0:06:40.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,有了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.01,0:06:44.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,西泽同学  可以下来一下吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.50,0:06:45.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是…是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.44,0:06:50.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,确实在这个时候  可以用玛莉亚小姐让我带上的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.28,0:07:11.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.88,0:07:14.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此  有这种装置
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.71,0:07:15.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢  玛莉亚小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.05,0:07:16.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.91,0:07:19.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小飒  来了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.47,0:07:24.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,恶心  这个机器真的是面向3D的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.88,0:07:26.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,Set on  手臂
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.32,0:07:29.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小飒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.66,0:07:37.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这…是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.12,0:07:48.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小飒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.26,0:07:50.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小飒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.39,0:07:52.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,给…给我记住
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.39,0:07:54.07,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,（玩偶出自「Yatterman」恶役三人组的波吉和阿祖，另外3人式的自行车也来自其中的逃脱用自行车）
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.67,0:07:56.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小飒  振作点
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.99,0:07:58.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小飒
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.04,0:08:02.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在那之后的一万几千年里
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.04,0:08:02.77,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,（这个台词来自「创圣之AQUARION」）
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.97,0:08:04.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,丧失记忆的小飒
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.84,0:08:08.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在宇宙空间中孤独地漂流着
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.06,0:08:13.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,发生了…什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.64,0:08:16.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎回来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.71,0:08:23.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是…梦吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.64,0:08:27.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对了  得快点把失忆题材的捏它录像带拿给大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.77,0:08:30.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,话说…我究竟是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.02,0:08:32.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小…小飒
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.35,0:08:34.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我…我马上就叫救护车
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.48,0:08:35.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不能死啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.31,0:08:36.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那…那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.00,0:08:40.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了  你没事吧  头还痛吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.74,0:08:44.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,呃…说回来  这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.20,0:08:46.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,居然是膝枕  我…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.27,0:08:47.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.72,0:08:50.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,痛痛痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.20,0:08:54.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我…我们好久没有像这样两人在一起的时候了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.91,0:08:55.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.18,0:08:59.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,呐…我一直都想问
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.36,0:09:01.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然那个时候被敷衍过去了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.32,0:09:05.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,其实我只对二次元有兴趣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.83,0:09:07.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,打击～
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.91,0:09:09.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,说真的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.17,0:09:14.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小…小飒  究竟是怎么看我的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.09,0:09:16.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,呐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.80,0:09:17.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,呃  那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.62,0:09:18.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,呐呐…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.37,0:09:22.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哇  我的头…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.86,0:09:23.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小…飒？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.28,0:09:26.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.16,0:09:28.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我究竟是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.53,0:09:31.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不…不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.62,0:09:33.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不小心又鬼使神差地…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.99,0:09:36.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就算再怎么样…这么破烂的演技
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.24,0:09:37.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,失…失忆
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.38,0:09:41.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小飒失忆了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.48,0:09:44.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,诶  她真的相信了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.33,0:09:48.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么办  我这可是第一次碰到真正的失忆啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.66,0:09:51.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…冬季恋歌 要是看了冬季恋歌就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.04,0:09:54.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要是看了秋日童话和夏日芬芳也好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.04,0:09:54.59,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,（秋日童话和夏日芬芳也是冬季恋歌导演的作品）
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.61,0:09:55.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,来晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.00,0:10:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,多谢惠顾
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.22,0:10:03.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  因为肚子饿了才叫的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.00,0:10:05.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,完全忘记了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.78,0:10:08.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  你莫非是…管家？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.04,0:10:10.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,呐  你是管家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.58,0:10:13.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我第一次见到真人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.78,0:10:16.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就是说  这位是大小姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.48,0:10:21.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那么  钱是由管家来支付吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.95,0:10:24.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那个  请支付吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.57,0:10:28.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,管…管家小飒
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.14,0:10:31.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在…在发什么呆啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.30,0:10:33.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,快点给钱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.30,0:10:41.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是…是  我明白了  大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.88,0:10:43.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.09,0:10:45.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我就是想看一次这个  就是这个
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.22,0:10:47.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这是红茶  大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.77,0:10:50.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,多谢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.19,0:10:58.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我…我是大小姐的管家吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.47,0:11:04.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对…对的  绫崎飒你…你是我西泽步的管家
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.17,0:11:09.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,糟糕了…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.88,0:11:10.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,麻烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.03,0:11:13.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,完全抓不到解释的时机
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.69,0:11:14.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,麻烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.73,0:11:17.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小飒似乎完全相信了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.85,0:11:19.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,总之  没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.37,0:11:20.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,船到桥头自然直嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.82,0:11:25.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.74,0:11:29.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  这难道是每半份味道都不一样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.26,0:11:32.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是的  这叫做half and half
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.75,0:11:34.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,呐  管家小飒
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.34,0:11:36.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不用客气  这边也吃吃看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.94,0:11:38.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是  我吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.24,0:11:41.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哎  这个真好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.92,0:11:45.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉是有生以来第一次吃到的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.63,0:11:47.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那只是鳀鱼味
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.55,0:11:49.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小飒没有吃过鳀鱼吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.25,0:11:51.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这个嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.41,0:11:54.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然在打工时有见到过
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.37,0:11:55.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不过…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.59,0:11:57.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真的很好吃  步大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.75,0:12:04.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这难道是神赐予我的礼物之时吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.36,0:12:06.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小飒
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.41,0:12:12.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,而且…难道你就是那小偷仓鼠
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.72,0:12:13.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.90,0:12:18.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  小飒  那是什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.27,0:12:19.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,别开奇怪的玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.06,0:12:21.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,诶  那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.32,0:12:23.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,才…才不会把小飒交给你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.02,0:12:27.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这人  这人是我的…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.36,0:12:30.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我重要的管家啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.97,0:12:31.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.09,0:12:35.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不好  这样的话就算强硬也得把事情说清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.02,0:12:37.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小飒
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.97,0:12:39.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉头很…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.00,0:12:39.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小飒
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.74,0:12:43.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好  现在是机会
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.84,0:12:48.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我说…啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.85,0:12:49.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小飒
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.87,0:12:52.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小飒居然会失忆
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.78,0:12:53.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这种事绝不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.86,0:12:57.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,等着我  小飒
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.90,0:13:01.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我一定会帮你把记忆取回来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.84,0:13:04.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,又…又被误解了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.95,0:13:08.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那个  我要装睡到什么时候才行呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.67,0:13:13.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs22}インドカレーは　かれえぞ{\r}\N印度咖喱可是　很辣的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.28,0:13:18.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs22}象は大きいだぞ　さむ{\r}\N象是很大的…好冷
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.88,0:13:20.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,听好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.81,0:13:24.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,现在开始进行绫崎飒的记忆补完计划
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.81,0:13:24.18,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,（计划名出自EVA的人类补完计划）
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.72,0:13:29.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,正好我今日对失忆方面进行了考察
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.87,0:13:32.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,而准备了各种方案
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.19,0:13:34.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,也请大家协助我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.28,0:13:37.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,感…感觉深处危险之中
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.79,0:13:42.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不过  大小姐为了漫画的构思而那么拼命
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.54,0:13:44.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如果这能成为什么灵感的话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.84,0:13:45.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.60,0:13:49.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,咦  这是哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.43,0:13:50.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.54,0:13:52.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哦  小飒  醒来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.54,0:13:53.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没…没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.90,0:13:54.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.17,0:13:55.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小飒
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.14,0:13:56.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.84,0:14:01.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你现在似乎因为失忆  而深信着自己是那仓鼠的管家了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.60,0:14:03.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,诶…那个  是的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.90,0:14:05.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我是那步大小姐的…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.79,0:14:06.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.82,0:14:07.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小飒
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.49,0:14:10.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你是我三千院凪的管家
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.24,0:14:11.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,正是如此
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.44,0:14:12.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,绫崎飒
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.76,0:14:14.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是悲伤啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.76,0:14:18.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就算尽全力  我也会把这个男人的记忆取回来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.83,0:14:21.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,克劳斯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.82,0:14:24.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你不会是认为我取不回小飒的记忆吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.08,0:14:26.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然很失礼  但正是如此
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.37,0:14:30.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,呵呵  有趣  我就接受这挑战
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.41,0:14:34.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你和我  究竟谁能取回小飒的记忆  来一决胜负吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.08,0:14:37.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哼  反正赢的会是我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.60,0:14:40.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…还比什么胜负…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.22,0:14:42.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如何  小飒  回忆起来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.62,0:14:46.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是你超喜欢的衣服哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.89,0:14:48.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什…什么喜欢…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.33,0:14:50.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这可怜的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.77,0:14:53.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在第八话里好像看到过又好像没看到过
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.93,0:14:57.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,打击…小飒他居然会有这种兴趣…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.45,0:15:00.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就这样  记忆恢复作战开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.59,0:15:04.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.63,0:15:06.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,快一击打倒它给我看看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.18,0:15:09.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我说  也不能老老实实的就这么成为饲料啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.11,0:15:12.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好  以这个作为契机
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.12,0:15:15.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,给我适可而止
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.94,0:15:28.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,打击…小飒居然有这种打虎的特技…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.94,0:15:29.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.66,0:15:30.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,呃  记忆啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.87,0:15:31.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好像还没有恢复
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.03,0:15:32.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,招式用错了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.10,0:15:35.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哼  看来还是未分胜负呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.62,0:15:36.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.49,0:15:38.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,凪大小姐和克劳斯在战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.57,0:15:39.99,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,（出自「ゲームセンターあらし」，小飒扮演的是主人公石野岚）
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.96,0:15:41.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,为了恢复小飒的记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.41,0:15:42.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,无情的战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.23,0:15:45.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,唔…记忆还没恢复吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.52,0:15:47.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这样的话  用冲击疗法吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.53,0:15:53.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,Stop…请住手  住手！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.33,0:15:54.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,下去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.34,0:15:58.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  忘了降落伞
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.93,0:16:02.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,克劳斯先生——！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.62,0:16:12.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才的叫喊…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.85,0:16:15.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,难道说小飒已经恢复记忆了？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.31,0:16:18.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,也许从一开始就根本没有失忆？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.11,0:16:21.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,超强的洞察力
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.71,0:16:22.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不  还没有
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.72,0:16:26.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那克劳斯的主意是不可能使小飒恢复记忆的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.51,0:16:27.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是…是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.70,0:16:35.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不过…小飒那家伙还没浮上来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.76,0:16:36.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,玛莉亚
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.33,0:16:37.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,微速前进
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.24,0:16:38.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,以防万一  搜索开始
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.73,0:16:41.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,再…再怎么说…这也做得过火了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.82,0:16:44.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…请原谅她吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.78,0:16:49.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小凪也是为了小飒  在以她自己的方式拼命努力
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.57,0:16:51.24,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,（EG Game Boy？）
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.24,0:16:53.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  小飒  没事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.08,0:16:55.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没事的话快回答
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.65,0:16:56.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.85,0:16:58.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,有点不甘心
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.67,0:17:01.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在我不知情的这段时间里
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.34,0:17:03.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,发生了这么多事情…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.80,0:17:05.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小飒与那孩子之间
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.15,0:17:17.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么回事  上次来钓鱼时有那座岛吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.94,0:17:19.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不…不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.21,0:17:20.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,总之先登录
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.54,0:17:22.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,玛莉亚  让船靠岸
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.48,0:17:23.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.82,0:17:28.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  我也去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.03,0:17:36.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,咦  什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.02,0:17:41.71,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,（这只巨龟原型来自赤松健的「LOVE HINA」）
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.11,0:17:46.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,难…难道是这也是由于三千院家不可思议生态圈而产生的？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.78,0:17:54.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.54,0:18:00.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,诶  居然在这种时候熄火了？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.28,0:18:11.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那个声音是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.66,0:18:14.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大小姐和西泽同学？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.04,0:18:22.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好…好可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.51,0:18:25.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这…这家伙是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.79,0:18:29.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,难道是岛神  是岛神吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.90,0:18:32.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,逃…逃吧  快点啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.18,0:18:35.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,刚…刚才摔的那一下  把腰扭了…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.09,0:18:44.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.61,0:18:46.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如果是小飒的话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.27,0:18:49.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如果是小飒的话  在这个时候一定…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.13,0:18:51.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.58,0:18:52.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在那边吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.82,0:19:07.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂…喂  快走开  这孩子是小飒重要的人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.09,0:19:08.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对她出手的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.96,0:19:10.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我绝对无法饶恕你！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.94,0:19:12.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,…差不多这样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.77,0:19:13.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,西泽同学
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.09,0:19:17.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  仓鼠  好意我心领了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.40,0:19:18.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,别在那里发软了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.42,0:19:19.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,住手  你这爬虫类
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.12,0:19:20.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小飒
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.51,0:19:22.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小飒？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.79,0:19:25.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,敢对这两人出手的话  我绝不会坐视不理的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.30,0:19:50.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大小姐  西泽同学
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.92,0:19:52.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没受伤…没受伤吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.55,0:19:54.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小飒
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.79,0:19:55.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.97,0:19:58.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,让两人深处险境  真是对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.20,0:20:02.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我…我作为三千院家的管家真是不合格
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.35,0:20:03.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小飒  记忆恢复了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.11,0:20:05.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了  小飒
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.23,0:20:07.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不过  我…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.36,0:20:11.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  你回到平常的这样就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.82,0:20:12.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.81,0:20:18.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是…是  十分感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.58,0:20:21.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好的  这样一来小飒记忆补完计划就完美结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.47,0:20:27.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不去送那位真的可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.23,0:20:32.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,唔…这回虽然不情愿  但却被那小动物救了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.54,0:20:34.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,总之  稍微让他们两人待一会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.65,0:20:35.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  好痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.07,0:20:40.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀  今天能知道小飒新的生活方式  真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.86,0:20:41.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.82,0:20:43.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,给你添了那么多麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.06,0:20:45.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,呐  小飒
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.50,0:20:47.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,还记得在公园里我问你的话吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.95,0:20:50.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,诶  是…是什么事情呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.40,0:20:51.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉头脑混乱了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.01,0:20:53.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,果然…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.67,0:20:57.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小飒很重视那个大小姐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.03,0:21:03.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不过  小飒对我来说也是非常…重要的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.27,0:21:05.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,西泽同学
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.97,0:21:07.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小飒  下回…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.76,0:21:08.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.59,0:21:10.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我们抽空去批萨店吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.09,0:21:13.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你没吃过鳀鱼味的批萨吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.76,0:21:15.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不过你绝对会喜欢的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.44,0:21:16.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我有这种预感
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.75,0:21:17.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉非常有自信
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.79,0:21:20.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,开玩笑的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.09,0:21:25.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那么  我们有缘再见吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.42,0:21:27.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,西泽同学…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.08,0:21:31.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在小飒心中留下了略带苦涩的回忆后
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.28,0:21:33.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,西泽离开了三千院家
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.42,0:21:35.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,而克劳斯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.53,0:21:37.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,超迷你…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.61,0:21:39.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就这样
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.45,0:21:42.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在自动操纵的情况下  飞向了被忘却的遥远彼方
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.32,0:21:45.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,次回将开始与新的剧情发展战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.21,0:23:21.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小凪和
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.12,0:23:22.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小飒的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.15,0:23:24.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,管家通讯
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.39,0:23:27.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,魔法变身  我是三千院凪
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.39,0:23:27.62,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,（出自「もえたん(萌单)」中女主角虹原变身的咒语）
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.68,0:23:28.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我是绫崎飒
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.01,0:23:29.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,时间过得真快
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.90,0:23:32.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这动画已经播放了半年了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.33,0:23:33.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  总算过了半年
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.11,0:23:34.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不过前面还漫长
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.15,0:23:36.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,今后也拜托了  小飒
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.68,0:23:37.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是  大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.71,0:23:39.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因此  下集开始将会是新OP
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.89,0:23:43.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,故事也会发展为管家们为了获得传说中的管家服而展开激烈战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.92,0:23:45.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,旋风管家要进入女装篇了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.77,0:23:47.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,诶  是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.39,0:23:48.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  总之大概就是这种感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.21,0:23:50.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,Byebye
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.43,0:23:55.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,管家战斗大会是什么  完全不懂是什么意思！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.81,0:23:57.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哼  正如你所见
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.43,0:24:00.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这是对我校管家们水平进行的一次评测
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.02,0:24:02.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这人就是…理事长
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.75,0:24:04.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,把我重要的葛叶大人…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.48,0:24:05.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你…无法饶恕
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.03,0:24:07.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,下集  旋风管家
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.72,0:24:09.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,「飒屹立于大地之上」
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.72,0:24:09.45,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,（来源于「机动战士高达」第一话标题）
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.59,0:24:16.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小飒  我…想亲眼看到你获得大会冠军的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.27,0:24:18.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你能存活下来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.27,0:24:18.76,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,（同样也出自「机动战士高达」）